{"tid":829897,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹颱風後上班塞爆港鐵，港鐵會有賠償嗎？","createTime":"2018-09-20T21:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T21:13:52.000Z","uid":47900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b75ac9c5ddc51335a100a65308f89cfbe1a8c6d5","tid":829897,"uid":47900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T21:13:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180708/58414225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F58414225&d=DwrpEjCuJ1DEr5WLGNw0pwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=9ffa6e2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F58414225&h=77fba1d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180708/58414225</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵延誤原來有得退車費？《蘋果》實測點回水<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人指，一般而言，所有港鐵乘客須繳付適當車費。如遇上列車服務中斷，港鐵會因應需要及現場情況，調整出閘機，乘客出閘時不會被扣除車費。就個別情況，車站職員會本著服務顧客的心，希望盡量幫助乘客，可能視個別情況作出個別安排。乘客如有任何有關事故期間的票務查詢，可向車站服務中心查詢，職員會作出適當跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當日咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}